room_title: Escape room "Kiss of the Dragon" by Escape Chambers in Des Moines
room_description: Hanzo Jiro runs the largest illegal gambling racket in all of Las Vegas. As the Oyubun, the "father," of one of the oldest and largest yakuza clans in the country, the Inagawa-Kai, the family's presence is notorious. Many yakuza of Kyushu Seido-Kai want to shift the balance of power. Short of all-out war, which would result in heavy losses for the Seido-Kai, there is only one option...
